Control statement : 
The statement or instructions are used to inform the computer to perform the task when a program is being executed.

There are four types of control statements : 
1. Sequential control statement 
   Input----->Formula Implementation-------->Output 
                     (Process)
   For ex : p,r,t     si=(p*r*t)/100        o/p : simple interest   

2. Conditional control statement
   (Decision control statement) 
3. Looping control statement 
4. Switch control statement  